# UI Components & Conventions

Todas las piezas de UI se construyen sobre la librería shadcn/ui; mantén la API y el estilo consistentes con sus patrones.

## Primitives
- Prefer shared UI primitives under [src/components/ui](mdc:src/components/ui) (shadcn/ui wrappers):
  - Buttons: [src/components/ui/button.tsx](mdc:src/components/ui/button.tsx)
  - Inputs: [src/components/ui/input.tsx](mdc:src/components/ui/input.tsx)
  - Selects: [src/components/ui/select.tsx](mdc:src/components/ui/select.tsx)
  - Labels: [src/components/ui/label.tsx](mdc:src/components/ui/label.tsx)
  - Checkboxes: [src/components/ui/checkbox.tsx](mdc:src/components/ui/checkbox.tsx)
  - Table: [src/components/ui/table.tsx](mdc:src/components/ui/table.tsx)
  - Theme toggle: [src/components/ui/theme-toggle.tsx](mdc:src/components/ui/theme-toggle.tsx)

## Forms
- Use shared form wrappers: [src/components/forms](mdc:src/components/forms) and [src/components/ui/form.tsx](mdc:src/components/ui/form.tsx).
- Feature-specific forms live under each feature (e.g., users/drivers/auth) and should compose primitives.

## App Chrome
- Header: [src/components/Header.tsx](mdc:src/components/Header.tsx)
- Sidebar: [src/components/Sidebar.tsx](mdc:src/components/Sidebar.tsx)

## Feature Components
- Core shared widgets: [src/features/core/components](mdc:src/features/core/components)
  - Modal: [src/features/core/components/modal.tsx](mdc:src/features/core/components/modal.tsx)
  - Data table: [src/features/core/components/data-table.tsx](mdc:src/features/core/components/data-table.tsx)
  - Action buttons: [src/features/core/components/action-buttons.tsx](mdc:src/features/core/components/action-buttons.tsx)
- Dashboard widgets: [src/app/dashboard/components](mdc:src/app/dashboard/components)
  - Total users card: [src/app/dashboard/components/TotalUsersCard.tsx](mdc:src/app/dashboard/components/TotalUsersCard.tsx)
- Charts & stats: [src/components/OverviewChart.tsx](mdc:src/components/OverviewChart.tsx), [src/components/MetricCard.tsx](mdc:src/components/MetricCard.tsx), [src/components/StatCard.tsx](mdc:src/components/StatCard.tsx)

Guidelines:
- Keep feature components self-contained. If a component becomes reusable across features, promote it to `src/components`.
- Keep style rules in [src/app/globals.css](mdc:src/app/globals.css). Prefer composition of primitives over ad-hoc elements.
- Extiende shadcn/ui localmente solo dentro de `src/components/ui`; evita dependencias directas a `@/components/ui` desde otros paquetes de shadcn.

